{
  "data": [
    {
      "algorithm": "object-detection",
      "createdAt": "{{faker 'date.recent' 365}}",
      "datasetId": 57,
      "datasetVersionId": {{faker 'random.number'}},
      "failureMsg": "To train a dataset and create a model, the dataset must contain at least 100 examples per label for test set",
      "language": "en_US",
      "modelId": "2KXJEOM3N562JBT4P7OX7VID2Q",
      "modelType": "",
      "name": "My Model - Version1",
      "object": "model",
      "progress": {{faker 'random.number'}},
      "status": "{{oneOf (array 'QUEUED' 'RUNNING' 'SUCCEEDED' 'FAILED' 'KILLED' 'FAILED_WITH_RETRIES')}}",
      "updatedAt": "{{faker 'date.recent' 365}}"
    }
  ],
  "object": "list"
}
responses.label: Success
